metadata.name: Strangers I Harbor
metadata.description:
Strangers I Harbor…
Ridiculed by Deception..
Lost in peer exuberance, tilted From Fate and Honor..
Delved in Stupidity and Insolence.. Tangled with despair and Anxiety.. was lost in the shell of a Simpleton.. 
Scavenged my thoughts and Might to find Myself, Imprisoned by my Ego.. Lost in the Dust… Oh my Kindness was taken for Granted.
Now I Realized, i harbored a Stranger..
